CustomField.formula:
IF(YEAR(Opportunity.Contract_Start_Date__c) = YEAR(Opportunity.Contract_End_Date__c),
Individual_Development__c,
(Individual_Development__c / 365) * Remaining_Days_In_Year__c
)

/* If the same year then show full value, if not the same year then
show the value scaled down to reflect only the amount falling in the starting FY*/
